org.javimmutable.collections.list

Class JImmutableArrayList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.javimmutable.collections.list.JImmutableArrayList<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<T>, Cursorable<T>, Indexed<T>, Insertable<T,JImmutableList<T>>, InvariantCheckable, IterableStreamable<T>, JImmutableList<T>, SplitableIterable<T>, Streamable<T>

    public class JImmutableArrayList<T>
extends Object
implements JImmutableList<T>, Serializable
    JImmutableList implementation using 32-way trees. The underlying trees, like the JImmutableList, only allow values to be inserted or deleted from the head or tail of the list.
    See Also:
